{"id":230441,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/06/维权网-上海维权人士探访冯正虎遭警察阻拦，何/","date":"2012-06-10T21:07:56Z","modified":"2012-06-10T21:07:56Z","title":"维权网 | 上海维权人士探访冯正虎遭警察阻拦，何茂珍被抓走（组图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><br />（维权网信息员王东见、晨晓报道）<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>日下午</span><span>，上海维权人士毛恒凤、王扣玛、陈建芳等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>余人，前往<span>政通路</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">240</span></span><span><span>弄</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span></span><span><span>号</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">302</span></span><span><span>室冯正虎的住处，欲探望多日无消息的冯正虎先生，但刚到小区附近，即遭到</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">50</span></span><span><span>多名上海警方及便衣的阻拦，何</span></span><span>茂珍被当场抓走。</span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span><span>据陈建芳说，冯正虎家的楼下有数名警察站岗，民众根本无法靠近。大家只能在街道上呼喊，但冯老师没有像往常那样听到呼喊出现在三楼的窗前，既无声音更看不到他的身影，这令大家万分焦急担忧。</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\">50</span></span><span><span>多名警察和便衣将大家驱散，我们无法靠近冯老师家的楼下。</span></span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span><span>毛恒凤在电话中说，几十名警察驱赶我们，警察强制要求大家上警车离开，最后何</span></span><span>茂珍被当场抓走，应该当晚就放了吧，一直没联系上。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>日</span><span>上午，本网信息员多次拨打何茂珍的电话，或关机或提示已转为联通小秘书，请留言。因此有关何茂珍的下落目前无法确认。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>自今年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>日至今冯正虎被囚禁在家已超过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">100</span><span>天，他家的电脑及手机都被抄走，家中的固定电话也常常受到干扰，所以他很难直接与外界联系，此前上海民众一两天都会到他居住的楼下为其送生活用品，冯正虎听到大家的呼喊也会到窗前对大家表示感谢。然而，自</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">26</span><span>日</span><span>开始，冯正虎连续被警方传唤，时间从早上</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>点到晚上</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>点左右，警方所谓的传唤一般不做笔录，冯正虎只是在派出所坐一天的冷板凳，警方的目的也许就是阻止他与民众的隔窗交往，从而阻断他与外界的一切联系。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>日</span><span>当天，冯正虎曾因腹泻不止被负责监控的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>名警察送到新华医院检查治疗。此后，就再也没有冯正虎的进一步消息。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>冯正虎被囚禁的现状，令维权界人士极为担忧他的身体健康状况及人身安危。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">(</span></div>\n<div></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-92LhEdYrHT0/T9QU0ySx9CI/AAAAAAAAIYs/5IdL0TQ167s/s1600/SAM_0109.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"184\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-92LhEdYrHT0/T9QU0ySx9CI/AAAAAAAAIYs/5IdL0TQ167s/s320/SAM_0109.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-f6G19OxOIEE/T9QU3KXtItI/AAAAAAAAIY0/zf8EE6_yDX8/s1600/SAM_0110.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-f6G19OxOIEE/T9QU3KXtItI/AAAAAAAAIY0/zf8EE6_yDX8/s320/SAM_0110.JPG\" width=\"228\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-uccgNPlsT8g/T9QU4w9lEBI/AAAAAAAAIY8/Zzh20pIZGwo/s1600/%E5%86%AF%E6%AD%A3%E8%99%8E%E5%AE%B6%E7%9A%84%E6%A5%BC%E4%B8%8B%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E7%AB%99%E5%B2%97,%E4%B8%8D%E8%AE%A9%E6%B0%91%E4%BC%97%E9%9D%A0%E8%BF%91.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"206\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-uccgNPlsT8g/T9QU4w9lEBI/AAAAAAAAIY8/Zzh20pIZGwo/s320/%E5%86%AF%E6%AD%A3%E8%99%8E%E5%AE%B6%E7%9A%84%E6%A5%BC%E4%B8%8B%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E7%AB%99%E5%B2%97,%E4%B8%8D%E8%AE%A9%E6%B0%91%E4%BC%97%E9%9D%A0%E8%BF%91.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>冯正虎家的楼下警察站岗,不让民众靠近</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-5572287226148532887?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\